      <title>阿达尼肯尼亚交易引发抗议、诉讼和听证会</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-28/adani-s-kenya-dealings-spark-protests-lawsuits-and-hearings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亿万富翁高塔姆阿达尼 (Gautam Adani) 提出运营肯尼亚的主要机场，这一提议引发了抗议、参议院听证会和针对该亚洲第二大富豪控制的集团的诉讼，尽管该集团获得了在东非国家建设高压输电线的协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-28/adani-s-kenya-dealings-spark-protests-lawsuits-and-hearings</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 28 Sep 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
